      "body" : "Note that MSDN recommends <i>against</i> usage of <a href=\"https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/system.runtime.compilerservices.methodimploptions(v=vs.110).aspx\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">MethodImplOptions.Synchronized</a> : Locking on the instance or on the type, as with the Synchronized flag, is not recommended for public types, because code other than your own can take locks on public types and instances. This might cause deadlocks or other synchronization problems."
